Title: AN ACT TO NAME "COMANDANTE QUEZON HIGHWAY" THE ROAD FROM BALANGA TO BAGAC, PROVINCE OF BATAAN.
Data:
[ Commonwealth Act No. 478, June 18, 1939 ]
AN ACT TO NAME "COMANDANTE QUEZON HIGHWAY" THE ROAD FROM BALANGA TO BAGAC, PROVINCE OF BATAAN.
Be it enacted by the national Assembly of the Philippines:
Section 1. The provincial road from Balanga to Bagac in the Province of Bataan is named as Comandante Quezon Highway.ℒαwρhi৷"
Section 2. This Act shall take effect on its approval.
Enacted, without Executive approval, June 18, 1939.
